{
  "texts": [
    "We further evaluated fixed pipeline deep research systems, including WebThinker (report mode) and Ai2 ScholarQA (Singh et al., 2025).",
    "Those baselines combine LMs with inference-time only pipelines to generate long-form reports.",
    "We ran their official codes with default or recommended configurations.",
    "(3) Closed deep research: we evaluated OpenAI Deep Research, Perplexity Sonar (reasoning), Perplexity Deep Research, and Claude-Sonnet Search.",
    "We also evaluate the latest Gemini3 Pro + Search (released on November 18), which is reported in its release to achieve superior performance compared to GPT-5 and other proprietary LMs."
  ]
}